== 發行 ==
電影於2015年12月25日在美國的限定地區上映，主要鎖定[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]，直到2016年1月8日才會在全國廣泛上映<ref>{{cite news|title=Celebrity Extra|last=Elavksy|first=Cindy|work={{link-en|Fort Myers Weekly|Fort Myers Weekly}}|agency={{link-en|King Features|King Features}}|date=2015-10-07}}</ref>。英國則排於2016年1月15日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.screendaily.com/5096974.article|title='The Revenant' sets UK release date|author=Michael Rosser|work={{link-en|Screen International|Screen International}}|date=2015-11-17|accessdate=2015-11-23|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123151036/http://m.screendaily.com/5096974.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===
《神鬼獵人》收穫了影評人普遍的好評，主要稱讚[[李奧納多·狄卡皮歐|李奧納多·狄卡皮歐]]和[[湯姆·哈迪|湯姆·哈迪]]的表現，以及導演伊納利圖與攝影師[[艾曼紐爾·盧貝茲基|艾曼紐爾·盧貝茲基]]的技術<ref name="Stephanie Zacharek 2016, p54">Stephanie Zacharek, TIME magazine, January 18, 2016, p54.</ref><ref name="MoraskiCBS_151225" /><ref name="newyorkerreview">{{cite web|last1=Lane|first1=Anthony|title=Wilder West "The Hateful Eight" and "The Revenant."|url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2016/01/04/wilder-west|accessdate=2016-02-08|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312144924/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2016/01/04/wilder-west|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，然而，電影的片長卻受到批評<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barber|first1=Nicholas|title=Film Review: How good is The Revenant?|url=http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20160114-film-review-how-good-is-the-revenant|accessdate=2016-02-08|ref=bbcBarberreview|archive-date=2020-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509113311/http://www.bbc.com/culture/story/20160114-film-review-how-good-is-the-revenant|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的318篇專業影評文章，其中259篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為81%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]7.9分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_revenant_2015/|title=The Revenant|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2016-02-22|archive-date=2015-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151129024310/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_revenant_2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的50篇評論文章，其中41篇予以好評，1篇差評，8篇褒貶不一，平均分為76（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-revenant-2015|title=The Revenant|work=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-01-19|archive-date=2015-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205044816/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-revenant-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/the-revenant-star-wars-the-force-awakens-weekend-box-office-1201678383/ |title=‘Force Awakens’ Crosses $800M On Saturday & Holds No. 1, ‘Revenant’ Taking No. 2 With $38M |work=Deadline.com |access-date=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225231229/https://deadline.com/2016/01/the-revenant-star-wars-the-force-awakens-weekend-box-office-1201678383/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《神鬼獵人》且在爛番茄及Metacritic上所評選的「2015年最佳電影」中，分別名列第79名與22名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-list-the-top-10-movies-of-2015|title=Best of 2015: Film Critic Top Ten Lists|website=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-01-10|archive-date=2015-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210190401/http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-list-the-top-10-movies-of-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/?year=2015|title=Top 100 Movies of 2015|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-12-16|archive-date=2015-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128230819/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/top/bestofrt/?year=2015|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/critics-pick-the-best-films-and-performances-of-2015-in-indiewires-annual-poll-20151214|title=Critics Pick the Best Films and Performances of 2015 in Indiewire's Annual Poll|author=Steve Greene|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=2015-12-14|accessdate=2015-12-16|archive-date=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215222649/http://www.indiewire.com/article/critics-pick-the-best-films-and-performances-of-2015-in-indiewires-annual-poll-20151214|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影在北美的總票房為1.836億美元，其他地區3.493億美元，全球總計5.33億美元<ref name="BOM"/>。[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]計算，若將總收入扣除所有預算，《神鬼獵人》[[淨利|淨利]]約6,160萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-revenant-profit-box-office-2015-1201721740/|title=No. 19 ‘The Revenant’ – 2015 Most Valuable Movie Blockbuster Tournament|author=Mike Fleming Jr|work=''Deadline.com''|date=2016-03-18|accessdate=2016-03-19|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214040012/https://deadline.com/2016/03/the-revenant-profit-box-office-2015-1201721740/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在美國及加拿大，電影於2015年12月25日[[有限上映|有限上映]]，週末在紐約市和洛杉磯的4家劇院中收穫了474,560美元，平均每家收益118,640美元，在劇院平均收入中名列第二<ref name="limited">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-force-awakens-christmas-weekend-box-office-record-joy-daddys-home-concussion-point-break-1201672899/ |title=‘Daddy’, ‘Joy’ & ‘Hateful Eight’ Reap Fortune As ‘Star Wars’ Halo Effect Impacts B.O…Can ‘Force Awakens’ Hit $1 Billion In U.S.? |publisher=Deadline.com |first1=Anthony |last1=D'Alessandro |first2=Anita |last2=Busch |date=2015-12-28 |accessdate=2015-12-31 |archive-date=2016-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605062051/http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-force-awakens-christmas-weekend-box-office-record-joy-daddys-home-concussion-point-break-1201672899/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位居《[[史帝夫賈伯斯_(電影)|史帝夫賈伯斯]]》的13萬美元之後（同樣在4家劇院有限上映）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/12/13/box-office-in-the-heart-of-the-sea-is-a-whale-of-a-fail-big-short-strikes-it-rich/|title=Box Office: 'In The Heart Of The Sea' Is A Whale Of A Fail, 'Big Short' Strikes It Rich|first=Scott|last=Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2015-12-13|accessdate=2015-12-13|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216064940/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/12/13/box-office-in-the-heart-of-the-sea-is-a-whale-of-a-fail-big-short-strikes-it-rich/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2週的上映期間中共收穫160萬美元，之後於2016年1月18日擴展到3,371家劇院廣泛發行<ref name="preview">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/the-revenant-star-wars-the-force-awakens-weekend-box-office-1201678383/|title=‘Revenant’ & ‘The Forest’ Begin B.O. Journey On Thursday; ‘Force Awakens’ To Cross $800M This Weekend – Box Office|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|work=''Deadline.com''|date=2016-01-08|accessdate=2016-01-08|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225231229/https://deadline.com/2016/01/the-revenant-star-wars-the-force-awakens-weekend-box-office-1201678383/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="box office">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/star-wars-force-awakens-the-revenant-leonardo-dicaprio-weekend-box-office-1201676277/ |title=‘The Revenant’ Will Bear Through Box Office Weekend Dominated By ‘Force Awakens’ – Preview |work=Deadline.com |access-date=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213152057/https://deadline.com/2016/01/star-wars-force-awakens-the-revenant-leonardo-dicaprio-weekend-box-office-1201676277/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

首映當天，《神鬼獵人》共收穫1,440萬美元，位居冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/01/09/box-office-star-wars-the-force-awakens-falls-to-2nd-place-on-friday-still-topping-800m/|title=Box Office: 'Star Wars: The Force Awakens' Falls To 2nd Place On Friday, Still Topping $800M|first=Scott|last=Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2016-01-09|accessdate=2016-01-09|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202074400/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/01/09/box-office-star-wars-the-force-awakens-falls-to-2nd-place-on-friday-still-topping-800m/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在首週末從3,375家劇院中進帳3,980萬美元，超過最初預測的70%，僅次於上映4週的《[[STAR_WARS：原力覺醒|STAR WARS：原力覺醒]]》（4,240萬美元）。該片為導演[[阿利安卓·崗札雷·伊納利圖|阿利安卓·崗札雷·伊納利圖]]生涯首映票房最高的作品，以及主演[[李奧納多·狄卡皮歐|李奧納多·狄卡皮歐]]與[[湯姆·哈迪|湯姆·哈迪]]的第四高<ref name="TheRev">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/the-revenant-star-wars-the-force-awakens-weekend-box-office-1201678383/|title=‘Force Awakens’ Crosses $800M & Holds No. 1, ‘Revenant’ Takes No. 2 With $38M – Final Sunday|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|work=''Deadline.com''|date=2016-01-10|accessdate=2016-01-11|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225231229/https://deadline.com/2016/01/the-revenant-star-wars-the-force-awakens-weekend-box-office-1201678383/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《神鬼獵人》的廣泛發行首週是2016年1月最高的首映週紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=01&p=.htm|title=TOP OPENING WEEKENDS BY MONTH (JANUARY)|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2016-01-11|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905111600/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=01&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，隔週則與《[[龍兄唬弟2|龍兄唬弟2]]》競爭，但被其擊敗，僅居第二。電影在第三個週末共進帳1,600萬美元，下降了49.7%，但票房位居榜首，因{{link-en|2016年1月美國暴風雪|January 2016 United States blizzard|東海岸大部分地區受暴風雪覆蓋}}，據報影響了許多電影的票房表現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4148&p=.htm|title='The Revenant' Weathers Snow Storm While Weekend's Newcomers Perform as Expected|first=Brad|last=Brevet|publisher=Box Office Mojo|date=2016-01-24|accessdate=2016-01-25|archive-date=2019-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524195700/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4148&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-winter-storm-jonas-858281|title=Box Office: Winter Storm Jonas Forces New York City, East Coast Theater Closures|first=Pamela|last=McClintock|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-01-24|accessdate=2016-01-25|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211174301/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-winter-storm-jonas-858281|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/box-office-dirty-grandpa-the-5th-wave-the-boy-during-storm-jonas-1201688827/|title=Superstorm 2016 – Box Office Iced Out Of About 8% To 10% In Receipts|first=Anita|last=Busch|work=''Deadline.com''|date=2016-01-24|accessdate=2016-01-25|archive-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806083457/https://deadline.com/2016/01/box-office-dirty-grandpa-the-5th-wave-the-boy-during-storm-jonas-1201688827/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/28/box-office-preview-kung-fu-panda-3-finest-hours-fifty-shades-of-black|title=Box office preview: Kung Fu Panda 3 eyes $40+ million opening|author=Devan Coggan|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-01-28|accessdate=2016-01-29|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211193400/https://ew.com/article/2016/01/28/box-office-preview-kung-fu-panda-3-finest-hours-fifty-shades-of-black/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。下週，《神鬼獵人》被同樣由福斯發行的電影《[[功夫熊貓3|功夫熊貓3]]》給超越。

